# MagicSquare Rule Entry

This project migrated detailed agent rules into `.cursor/rules/*.mdc`.

Primary rule files:

- `magicsquare-project.mdc`
- `magicsquare-python-code-style.mdc`
- `magicsquare-ecb-architecture.mdc`
- `magicsquare-tdd-testing.mdc`
- `magicsquare-forbidden.mdc`
- `workflow-automation.mdc` (kept as-is by request)

Use the `.cursor/rules` files as the source of truth for behavior and standards.
